    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, when you say the report is outdated, do you mean the 3-day window is wrong? I'm looking at the timestamp right now and it definitely looks like it was exposed for a while. \n\nAlso, if we call it a \"glitch,\" isn't there a risk the tech reporters will dig deeper and find out it was actually a misconfigured S3 bucket? I'm worried that if we're too vague, it'll look like we're hiding something, which would be even worse for brand trust. Can we get more specific with the framing so it sounds more controlled?",
